'''''Callet'dira''''' was a musical aria used to motivate [[Gacerite]] [[Soldier/Legends|soldiers]] into a more efficient frenzy before battle. It was played by the [[Musicmaker]]s of each military unit.<ref name="AE">''[[Alien Encounters]]''</ref>

